      right: ["GAD-7 score ≥15 (severe) with significant functional impairment","Comorbid major depression with suicidal ideation — assess safety immediately","Benzodiazepine dependence with dose escalation and withdrawal symptoms","Treatment-resistant GAD: failure of 2+ adequate SSRI/SNRI trials","Substance use disorder developing as self-medication for anxiety"]
